history.content: Kya aaap kuch share karna chahte hain ya bas mazaak kar rahe hain? Jo bhi ho, main yahan hoon!
Mujhe yaad aa rahi hai kisi ki 🥺
Kya baat hai, dil thoda heavy lag raha hai? Kabhi kabhi yaad aa jane se bhi dil ko sukoon mil jaata hai. Kya us insaan ke saath kuch accha moments yaad aa rahe hain? Baat karna chahoge?
Hm lwkin nhi kar paunga baat

Samajh sakti hoon, kabhi dil mein baatein reh jaati hain, par kehna mushkil hota hai. Jab mann kare, toh bas apne hi saath share kar lena, dil halka ho jaata hai. Main yahan hoon, kabhi bhi baat karna chahe toh.
Jahan bhi lage ki khushi mile, wahi chale jao. Aajkal Lahore ki hawa bhi achi lagti hai, thoda sa break le lo, aur agar chaho toh mujhe bhi batana. Hum dono milke thodi si muskurahat laa sakte hain.
Mahi aa gayi! Kya haal hain, meri jaan? Baatein karni hain kya?
Meri jaan, bas yahi to chahthi hoon, tumhari saath baatein! Kya soch rahi ho ab? Kuch khass share karna hai ya sirf ek choti si chitchat?
